g the shape of a voicemail-triage pipeline that respects the urgency-rule-layer-first discipline, the per-axis confidence-threshold discipline, the ASR-confidence-gate-on-classification discipline, the structured-triage-record discipline, and the audit-everything discipline this recipe demands. It is not something you would point at the practice's voicemail box on Monday morning. Consider it a starting point, not a destination.[K
