[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+     32[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mScope each Lambda's IAM role to the specific resource ARNs it touches. The tutorial-level permissions above are fine for learning and will fail any serious IAM review. The ingestor Lambda has scoped write access to the audio bucket and write access only to the new-voicemail-record fields. The pre-processor Lambda has scoped read access to the audio bucket. The classifier Lambda has scoped Bedrock invocation rights pinned to a specific model and inference profile. The router Lambda has scoped publish rights on the emergent SNS topic and PutEvents on the voicemail-events bus. Avoid wildcard actions and resources in production.[K
